Name: Cannabis Farmer Strain Master
About the game: Cannabis Farmer Strain Master is a Marijuana growing simulator game where you will put your master grower skills to test. Grow strains, learn about them, and sell them to local dispensaries. Unlock dozens of different strains (with more to come!) and level up as you grow and sell your way to Strain Master status. Unlock new stores to sell at. Everchanging environmental conditions such as rain that affects plant quality. Use supplements like Mychorize, Sea kelp, organic, chemical fertilizer, and final flush to increase quality of buds. Test your grow skills to reach different quality levels for your plants just like real life growing, meaning higher profit and unlockables! Harvest your plants with a variety of tools including fun things like ninja swords and ninja stars for some added harvesting fun! Different leaf textures, size, height, and shape. 3D spatial sounds immerse you in the grow! Daily Tasks. Earn money selling and unlock extras like bongs at the dispensaries and more to discover! VR Support coming in near future
